title: Teaching Squat Form
content: I’ve been teaching my daughter Olivia how to squat, a gift she lost, courtesy of all the sitting kids do in school. So we’re back to square one on form.

title: Bodyweight Squats
content: I’ve told her she needs to do 500/week of bodyweight squats, and once she hits about 10,000, she might be ready to do some light goblet squats.

title: Inspiration from a Video
content: Anyway, recently I was looking at Twitter and saw this video. Some of you may have seen it, also. I said, “Hey Olivia, I want to show you something,” and she came over. I said, “What do you notice about this?” Olivia: She’s a girl? Me: And? Olivia: She’s young? Me: And? Olivia: She’s strong? Me: AND??? Olivia: Oh my god….
